{
  "stem": "24466.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And 1,000-- about 1,500 people went out, because the-- the workers with the wives and the-- and the families out from ghetto and separate.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They established two blocks on the-- on the name, Kailis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "K-A-I-L-I-E-I-S-- Kailis.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From ghetto one, that was quite-- that was on the periphery-- how to call it?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The periphery of the town, Vilna--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--not far from the factory where the [NON-ENGLISH]-- the [NON-ENGLISH] had been working, a little bit further from the tanneries.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were also going in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's mean in a group-- in groups-- to work, and from work, coming back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--oh, it was-- it was a lot better, because every family got a room for themself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were three room or four room-- three, I believe-- a room-- flats, you know, with the-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] --entrance-- a big entrance, a bathroom, a kitchen, and so on.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So all of this in every flat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was three families living.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were two blocks-- block number one, and block number two there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in block number one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had the room that was on the second floor-- on the second floor--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the first room against the entrance of that flat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the beginning, that was only by police in-- Jewish police what was formed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that took only nearly a year that the SS made from that arbeiter block, [NON-ENGLISH] They make concentrations arbeiter block number one and number two.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, that was a way to-- what they are calling the guards on--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--on towers, yes, on the four-- on the four corners of that block.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were-- and they went by the entrance, a guard, a SS man that the times were the worst, that time.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
